OL,3,CUS actor in legal battle with council
OL,4,Cto gain control of his ancestral home
OL,6,FAn American actor who has been
OL,7,Frenovating his ancestral home after it
OL,8,Ffell into disrepair is taking the
OL,9,Flocal council to court in an attempt
OL,10,Fto gain ownership.
OL,12,FHopwood DePree is began work on Grade
OL,13,FII-listed Hopwood Hall in Middleton,
OL,14,FGreater Manchester, 2017, but was
OL,15,Flocked out of the building by Rochdale
OL,16,FBorough Council (RBC) almost a year
OL,17,Fago.
