OL,3,CUS actor in legal battle with council
OL,4,Cto gain control of his ancestral home
OL,6,FHe said this was granted in October
OL,7,F2022 for the hall to be used for
OL,8,F"events, hospitality, tours,
OL,9,Feducation, cafe and shop".
OL,11,FBut the actor said that in November
OL,12,Flast year, RBC locked him and his team
OL,13,Fof volunteers out of the building and
OL,14,Fhas since refused to transfer
OL,15,Fownership of the property.
OL,17,FMr DePree claims RBC has broken their
OL,18,Flegal agreement by saying that he must
OL,19,Fget planning permission for physical
OL,20,Fworks, but did not specify this
OL,21,Fpreviously.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@YO]
