OL,3,CUS actor in legal battle with council
OL,4,Cto gain control of his ancestral home
OL,6,FIn a witness statement, he said: "It
OL,7,Fwas never my understanding that any
OL,8,Fphysical works would be required that
OL,9,Fwould require planning permission of a
OL,10,Fdifferent type, nor that listed
OL,11,Fbuilding consent would be part of this
OL,12,Fprocess."
OL,14,FAn RBC spokesperson declined to
OL,15,Fcomment on current legal proceedings
OL,16,Fbut pointed to a statement from
OL,17,FNovember which said the council had
OL,18,Fdecided not to extend the length of
OL,19,Fthe agreement because a "viable
OL,20,Fbusiness case and funding strategy has
OL,21,Fnot been forthcoming".
