OL,4,Cto gain control of his ancestral home
OL,6,FIt also said RBC has invested #1.7
OL,7,Fmillion into the building and is
OL,8,Facting "to protect the public monies
OL,9,Finvested to date".
OL,11,FMr DePree said more than #500,000
OL,12,Fearmarked for renovation had been lost
OL,13,Fbecause of RBC's delays and that the
OL,14,Fmorale of his team is "extremely low".
OL,16,FHe wants a High Court judge to declare
OL,17,Fthat he has fulfilled his obligations
OL,18,Funder the agreement and is therefore
OL,19,Fentitled to ownership.
