OL,3,CUS actor in legal battle with council
OL,4,Cto gain control of his ancestral home
OL,6,F"Even though it was in a derelict
OL,7,Fstate, I could see its beauty, history
OL,8,Fand spirit.
OL,10,F"It felt like a place that could be
OL,11,Fresurrected and reopened to the
OL,12,Fcommunity with visitors being able to
OL,13,Fjoin us from near and afar."
OL,15,FMr DePree added that he was "shocked
OL,16,Fat the behaviour" of RBC, which he
OL,17,Fclaimed had "never explained to me why
OL,18,Fthey decided to withdraw" from the
OL,19,Fagreement.
